snippet.title: Commodore 64 Longplay Telarium Dragonworld 1984
snippet.description:
Popular theme from the era and probably even today. The playing of the music notes was sort of unique for a word game... Interestingly the monkey was brown and not green, as described.

It is a shame the loading times from most Telarium game are very slow. A .crt conversion would really help here.
